ITEM: The PlayStation 5 console offers lightning-fast loading, deeper immersion, and an all-new generation of incredible PlayStation games with an 825GB SSD for faster and more efficient performance.

The PlayStation 4 console delivers powerful graphics and speed, deeply integrated social capabilities, connected gaming, intelligent personalization, and innovative second-screen features with a 1TB HDD.
The DualSense wireless controller for PlayStation 5 offers immersive haptic feedback, dynamic adaptive triggers, and a built-in microphone, all integrated into an iconic design.
The PlayStation VR headset provides an immersive gaming experience, bringing you closer to the action than ever before with a high-definition OLED display and 3D audio.
The PlayStation 4 Pro console enhances your gaming experience with faster frame rates, stunning 4K visuals, and HDR technology for brilliant graphics and lifelike details.
The Xbox Series X console delivers the fastest, most powerful Xbox performance ever, featuring 12 teraflops of processing power, 1TB SSD storage, and true 4K gaming.
The Xbox Series S console offers next-gen performance in the smallest Xbox ever, with an all-digital experience, 512GB SSD storage, and a streamlined design.
The Xbox One console provides a complete home entertainment system, with a 1TB HDD, advanced multiplayer capabilities, and access to a vast library of games.
The Xbox Wireless Controller offers precise control, enhanced comfort, and seamless connectivity with Xbox Series X, Xbox One, and Windows 10 devices.
The Xbox Game Pass Ultimate subscription service provides unlimited access to over 100 high-quality games, including Xbox Live Gold and EA Play membership.
The Nintendo Switch console offers versatile gaming with its hybrid design, allowing you to play at home or on the go with detachable Joy-Con controllers and a vibrant display.
The Nintendo Switch Lite is a compact, lightweight handheld console perfect for gaming on the go, featuring integrated controls and compatibility with the Nintendo Switch library.
The Nintendo Switch Pro Controller offers a premium controller experience, with a comfortable grip, motion controls, and HD rumble for immersive gameplay.
The Nintendo Ring Fit Adventure combines fitness and adventure gaming, providing a fun and interactive way to stay active with a unique Ring-Con and Leg Strap accessories.
The Nintendo Switch OLED Model features a vibrant 7-inch OLED screen, enhanced audio, and an adjustable stand for the ultimate gaming experience at home or on the go.
